summary: Adds three free mannequins to the vanilla player house, Breezehome.
descriptionHtml:
STEAM VERSION: [url=http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=309243499]http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=309243499[/url]




[b]--Summary--[/b] 
In short, what this mod adds to your game are three, free mannequins to the Breezehome vanilla player house in Whiterun. All three are upstairs awaiting your outfits. 

They don't require a house upgrade to be added, just download this mod and they're there. 



I always felt like the Breezehome was missing this vital game asset so I added them in there myself while also attempting to not overcrowd the place.
author: Kyle8497
